eetings Africa; and EXSA’s EXSA-llence Award for Best Stand Award in the 51-100 m² category, for two stands – Dr Reddy’s and SANParks.“We’re delighted with these results, which reflect the talent and dedication of our team,” says Justin. “The competition was incredibly stiff this year – especially in the Green Awards category where there was an increase in the number of entries. This makes these achievements even more meaningful.” For more information, please contact:Zoe Broad  | Scan Display Marketing Manager | zoe@scandisplay.co.zabRev('brev-f9c3e6d2-eda9-49ac-88cf-f8d22ece2386', '>a/\<az.oc.yalpsidnacs@eoz>"az.oc.yalpsidnacs;46#&eoz:otliam"=ferh a<')  | +27 11 447 4777Visit: www.scandisplay.co.za | www.aaxo.co.za | www.exsa.co.za